# Managed by CivPVP-Infra. Key-only SSH access.
# Named 00- so it sorts first: sshd uses first-match-wins across
# sshd_config.d/*.conf, and Ubuntu cloud images ship a 50-cloud-init.conf
# that sets "PasswordAuthentication yes". This file must precede it.
PasswordAuthentication no
PermitRootLogin no
PubkeyAuthentication yes
KbdInteractiveAuthentication no
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
UsePAM yes
